OL,3,CMan banned from keeping dogs following
OL,4,CXL Bully attack
OL,6,FA Cheltenham man has been given a
OL,7,Fsuspended prison sentence and banned
OL,8,Ffrom keeping dogs for life, following
OL,9,Fan XL Bully attack.
OL,11,FGloucester Crown Court heard how the
OL,12,Fvictim had been walking his dog on 7
OL,13,FMay 2023 and had approached a communal
OL,14,Fgarden that Phillip Ilott was in with
OL,15,Fhis dog, which was not on a lead.
OL,17,FOnce inside, Ilott's dog approached
OL,18,Fthem and attacked the victim's dog by
OL,19,Flatching onto its neck.
