OL,6,FAs the victim tried to intervene and
OL,7,Fstop the attack, Ilott's dog bit him
OL,8,Fon the hand, causing deep puncture
OL,9,Fwounds and bleeding which required
OL,10,Fhospital treatment.
OL,12,FThe victim's dog sustained injuries to
OL,13,Fits neck and body and was taken to the
OL,14,Fvet to be treated.
OL,16,FIlott, aged 32 and from the Monkscroft
OL,17,Farea, pleaded guilty to being the
OL,18,Fowner in charge of a dog dangerously
OL,19,Fout of control causing injury.
