OL,6,FA Gloucestershire Police spokesperson
OL,7,Fsaid: "The court also ordered that the
OL,8,Fdog be humanely destroyed."
OL,10,FPC Rebekah Tristram said: "Ilott
OL,11,Ffailed to keep his dog under control
OL,12,Fand as a result, a man was attacked
OL,13,Fand sustained serious injuries.
OL,15,F"The victim's dog was also injured
OL,16,Fduring the attack, which must have
OL,17,Fbeen incredibly distressing for the
OL,18,Fanimal and for his owner to witness.
