OL,3,CMan banned from keeping dogs following
OL,4,CXL Bully attack
OL,6,F"I welcome Ilott's sentence and hope
OL,7,Fthat it will serve as a warning to all
OL,8,Fdog owners that, regardless of the
OL,9,Fbreed of dog, all pets need to be kept
OL,10,Funder control in public places.
OL,11,FFailure to do so can lead to some
OL,12,Fhorrific outcomes.
OL,14,F"We will continue to take all reports
OL,15,Fof suspected irresponsible dog
OL,16,Fownership seriously and will act on
OL,17,Fall information provided."
